Refrigerants | Hudson Technologies








































            Search for:          


 






 









 Refrigerants 
Home > Refrigerants 





Largest Inventory Selection
At Hudson Technologies, we offer one of the largest refrigerant inventory selections in the country, along with a convenient nationwide network of distributors. All our refrigerant products meet or exceed ARI- 700 purity standards. For your convenience, they also are available in all standard industry sizes, including tanker and ISO containers for bulk delivery.
Over the past 25+ years, we’ve provided hundreds of thousands of pounds of emergency, after-hours refrigerant shipments to get our customers up and running as quickly as possible. We can be reached 24 hours a day, seven days a week for routine and emergency shipments. In fact, even routine orders placed before 1 p.m. EST will be shipped that same day.
In addition to supplying refrigerants, we purchase and buyback virtually any used CFC, HCFC and HFC refrigerants at a competitive price. As part of this buyback program, we provide empty recovery cylinders and make freight arrangements. Through recovery and reclamation, Hudson has ensured that millions of pounds of refrigerant have been reclaimed to AHRI standards.  Having one of only 3 ARI approved laboratories Hudson can ensure that all reclaimed refrigerant meets or exceeds ARI-700 requirements and eliminates any quality concerns with the use of reclaimed refrigerant. This enables reclaimed refrigerant to be reused and has reduced the impact of new refrigerant production on the environment.  Our buyback and reclamation of refrigerants enables Hudson to continue to supply the HVAC and Refrigeration industries with numerous refrigerants that are no longer manufactured, but are still used in equipment such as R-11, R-12, R-133 and R-114 to name just a few.
To learn more about our Refrigerant Capabilities click the Play Now button to watch our video.





 


































