Hudson Technologies








































            Search for:          


 






 









 Home 







At Hudson Technologies, we provide complete life cycle management of refrigerants and our commitment to environmental stewardship is core to everything we do.  At all stages of the refrigerant life cycle, Hudson has proven, reliable programs that meet your needs. From initial sale through recovery, reclamation and reuse, peak operating performance of equipment through energy efficiency and emergency air conditioning and refrigeration system repair, to final refrigerant disposal and carbon credit trading we provide environmentally sustainable solutions to your refrigerant needs.
We invite you to get to know us better by browsing our website or contacting us. We’re ready to serve you – and to help you with any refrigerant need.




Refrigerants
At Hudson, we offer one of the largest inventory selections in the country, along with a convenient nationwide network of distributors. All of our products meet or exceed ARI- 700 purity standards.

 


On-site Refrigerant Services
 When you have a refrigerant issue, there’s no need to send in samples, wait for analysis, and deal with costly downtime for your equipment. Instead, we bring the solution right to your doorstep.

 


Refrigerant Reclaim
With patented and proprietary technology, Hudson Technologies is the industry leader in refrigerant reclamation services.

 




Global Energy Services
Engineering, predictive and preventative maintenance, optimization software and services, training, and utility system assessments for commercial, institutional and industrial customers.

 



Investor Relations
Hudson Technologies is committed to employing its engineering and chemistry know-how to provide our customers with economic solutions that also provide significant environmental benefits to all. 

 


Wholesaler Online Refrigerant Store
Hudson Technologies online refrigerant store for our current wholesale customers. Place your orders for refrigerant directly with Hudson here.

 









