 Request for Quote



 





Engineered solutions for your  enclosure needs. Hudson Technologies has leading capabilities and solutions for your custom deep drawn metal enclosures, case, header and metal diaphragms. Request for Quote 






Our Services Hudson Technologies' core capabilities include expertise with a variety of high performance metals, including stainless steel and titanium, along with aluminum, aluminized steel, cold rolled steel, brass, copper, HY-MU 80 (other shielding alloys available), nickel, cupro nickel and more. 
 

 
Custom Capabilities & Components 



 
Medical Products 



 
Metal Diaphragms 



 
