Facilities List Hudson Technologies houses machines built to meet your specific needs. View Here 


About Us Hudson Technologies is a leading U.S. green manufacturer of deep drawn metal enclosures, or cases, and stampings, including metal diaphragms. Design engineers turn to Hudson Technologies for custom enclosures and metal diaphragms for their technology whether they need a prototype or high-volume production. Read More 
 







Industries we serve include: Aerospace, Medical, Pressure Transducters, Semi Conductor, Commercial Battery, and Capacitors

 

